  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/11f069e774a64f1d058597ebf6cad570.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/11f069e774a64f1d058597ebf6cad570.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Turmoil Uprising: Dynasty》is a rogue-lite casual game, player needs to make decisions to grow your character, overcome challenges from mobs and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game now features 15 heroes, each has unique perks and characteristics. Players can make their choices to enhance the hero base on strengths and weaknesses of the hero, to defeat powerful foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/bcbdd48de57f6854dac59a13ff72248d.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/bcbdd48de57f6854dac59a13ff72248d.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=1066 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use gold earned from play throughs to buy permamnent upgrades to gain advantage for your next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/51847651c1125531847fe9eeabceb8f8.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/51847651c1125531847fe9eeabceb8f8.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize every power-up, overcome enemies as you survive through waves of attacks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own strategy, climb up the legendary leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to rise above the turmoil?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/c983f05e5946dd3d70edc35326e57b97.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/c983f05e5946dd3d70edc35326e57b97.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/11f069e774a64f1d058597ebf6cad570.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/11f069e774a64f1d058597ebf6cad570.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Turmoil Uprising: Dynasty》is a rogue-lite casual game, player needs to make decisions to grow your character, overcome challenges from mobs and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game now features 15 heroes, each has unique perks and characteristics. Players can make their choices to enhance the hero base on strengths and weaknesses of the hero, to defeat powerful foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/bcbdd48de57f6854dac59a13ff72248d.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/bcbdd48de57f6854dac59a13ff72248d.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=1066 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use gold earned from play throughs to buy permamnent upgrades to gain advantage for your next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras/51847651c1125531847fe9eeabceb8f8.avif?t=1746910992\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984380/extras_big/51847651c1125531847fe9eeabceb8f8.avif?t=1746910992 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize every power-up, overcome enemies as you survive through waves of attacks!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create 